*Kit, a new female otter bot, popped her head out of the water as two bots (SINESIS and SINISTER) fell into the lake, fighting, trying to kill each other. She had been swimming to try and get to the Ark, looking for a fight, but this was good!!*

*The otter bot swims over to where the are and shouts* "SURPRISE!" *When they continued fighting, she transforms, her natural floating abilites keeping her up. She lifts up a gun*

"Heeeeeyyyaaaaaaa!!!!" *She yells and aims it at the nearest one of them*
